{"type": "article", "id": 10241, "title": "虚拟现实 Dior Eyes", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-01T07:41:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 2, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021258074vFTn0ZzOKJ1usME.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tDior 最近推出了虚拟现实设备 “Dior Eyes”，用户戴上它，可以身临其境地去 Dior 时装秀的后台近距离进行观看，包括化妆师为模特化妆的过程，模特上台前在做什么等全方位的后台景象，“Dior Eyes ” 将于今年 6 月正式发布，将会在全球部分精品店内提供产品体验。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125804aKqleZfGPJtEAsMU.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.5794621\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125804nYt9Scfp3DvoJL0b.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.61613692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125805DSGoNyEB5s6WKhdz.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.58190709\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125805YuG6kgpLSPtn5ml2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702125806koJN74qje9ZAIvPp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.54400978\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n"}